      <section name='diggingbar'>

         <para number='1' comment='324-DOWN-got Digging Bar'>
         Jamming the bar under one corner of the statue, you pry and it begins to move. Getting a new purchase on the bar and pushing hard, the statue moves out of the way and you can see into the hole. There is a ladder. There is also a very pungent smell coming from the hole. Holding your nose you climb down.
         </para>

         <para number='2' comment='694-get Digging Bar'>
         Stepping around the boxes, you grab the digging bar. It is heavier than it looked. You will have to carry it with 2 hands.
         </para>

         <para number='3' comment='drop Digging Bar'>
         The digging bar hits the ground and before you can react, the Oldman comes along and says, "I'll Take that." He bends over and grabs it and is gone.
         </para>

         <para number='4' comment='324-DOWN-no Digging Bar'>
         You try as hard as you can but the Statue will not move. If you just had something to use as a lever you could get it done.
         </para>

